      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I am using Kontera as in-text advertising from a long time and had very good relationship with them. I was also making some <a href="http://www.jimkarter.com/2008-04-29-crossing-9000month-with-kontera.html" target="_new">good money</a> with them till recently. I had fixed CPM deal with them.</p>
<p>Few days back <a href="http://www.jimkarter.com/go/infolinks.php" rel="nofollow">infolinks</a> invited me to join and test their program for a while. I tested their program for 3 days and the results was wonderful. It created me much more money than what Kontera was creating. So I decided to move to infolinks from Kontera.</p>
<p>But Kontera didn&#8217;t want to loose me, so that offered me even better fixed CPM rate than infolinks. But they could not sustain it as they were not making as much money from my sites as they were paying me. So they moved me back to the CPC based plan.</p>
<p>So I moved my biggest sites from Kontera to <a href="http://www.jimkarter.com/go/infolinks.php" rel="nofollow">infolinks</a>. Infolinks is making me at-least 3 times of what Kontera is making me in CPC model.</p>
<p>My recent <strong>eCPM with infolinks is $3.00</strong> which Kontera can never even touch I think.</p>
<p><strong>Infolinks Affiliate Program</strong><br />
Info has their affiliate program which is not yet available to general public. You can contact their support to get it enabled for you. This program is really wonderful and out of the world. Here is the payment structure.</p>
<ol>
<li>For a small publisher referred through you, <strong>you get paid $25</strong>.</li>
<li>If the publisher creates more than 10,000 impression per day, <strong>you get paid $100</strong>.</li>
<li>If the publisher creates more than 100,000 impressions per day, <strong>you get paid $1000</strong>.</li>
</ol>
<p>Wow! that is really wonderful. Its not very difficult to find publishers with more than 10,000 page view (please note, its page view and not uniques) per day. Also, on an average I think you will get 1 in 25 publishers who will be getting more than 100,000 page views a day.</p>
<p>So overall, <a href="http://www.jimkarter.com/go/infolinks.php" rel="nofollow"><strong>INFOLINKS ROCKS</strong> - Join Now</a>.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.jimkarter.com/go/infolinks.php" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.infolinks.com/images/infolinksLogo.gif" border=0></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
